==Class Data Structure==

Class data is stored at bank $C2, starting at $C20000.

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 byte || Class ID
|-
| $01 || 1 byte || Base HP growth rate
|-
| $02 || 1 byte || Base MP growth rate
|-
| $03 || 1 byte || Base Strength growth rate
|-
| $04 || 1 byte || Base Agility growth rate
|-
| $05 || 1 byte || Base Vitality growth rate
|-
| $06 || 1 byte || Base Intelligence growth rate
|-
| $07 || 1 byte || Base Luck growth rate
|-
| $08 || 2 bytes || Equipment flags (weapon types)
|-
| $0a || 2 bytes || Equipment flags (armor types)
|-
| $0c || 4 bytes || Spell learning table pointer
|}

