===Sage Spells===
Sages learn both Pilgrim and Wizard spells at combined level progression.

==Special Class: Sage==

Sages can only be obtained by:
# Bringing a Book of Satori to Dharma Temple with a level 20+ character
# A Goof-Off at level 20+ will automatically be allowed to become a Sage

The Book of Satori is consumed upon use.

